Job_Description:
Overview: The Senior DevOps Engineer will strive to advance our “Automate Everything” program. This role will drive the implementation of our no touch CI/CD pipeline through design, and construction, and implementation. Additionally this role will mentor junior staff on the CICD pipeline.
Duties and Responsibilities:
Seek opportunities to automate CI/CD pipeline and remove waste;
Provide emergency support as necessary, including after-hours;
Using Linux Automation and Configuration systems;
Experience with web security and patching strategies;
Experience with cloud backup strategies;
